               <odd id="aspace_e46d23d8a36066723deddc66e9c6671b">
                  <head>General</head>
                  <p>This report lists courses which Eaton proposed to offer and contrasts the equipment for botanical studies at Harvard and at Yale. With this is a statement also in his hand concerning the "Botany optional" at Yale, which may be Eaton's copy of Porter's note on the subject. 3 p. and 1 l.</p>
               </odd>
